Massive thank you to the developer for finally updating the app (March 2018). It's working much better now. It's almost as good as Super Retro 16 now. EDIT: YES! Everything works after the last update! Big shout out to the devs! Thanks guys! This emulator has a lot of potential, but needs some work on the actual emulation of the games. Tried different roms of the same game, some work better than others, but some glitches persist. Contra en SMB1 are the biggest let down for me. Other than that, you get all the good stuff from Super Retro 16: good controller support, best UI of any emulator app, etc.
